msgstr "and I’ve given up confusion/renounced it/let it go/abandoned it/relinquished it/forsaken it/thrown it aside and my mind is free from the hindrance of sensual desire and my mind is free from the hindrance of ill-will and my mind is free from the hindrance of confusion,” while actually saying, “I attained the first absorption,” then, if the listener understands, he commits an offense entailing expulsion when three conditions are fulfilled;"

