#. REF: sc169, ms1V_702
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.25"
msgid "Tīhākārehi … pe … sattahākārehi yaṃ tvaṃ āgamma vihāraṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "If he lies in full awareness, saying, “The monk to whom you gave a dwelling …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.26"
msgid "cīvaraṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "to whom you gave robe-cloth …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.27"
msgid "piṇḍapātaṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "to whom you gave almsfood …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.28"
msgid "senāsanaṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "to whom you gave a dwelling …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.29"
msgid "gilā­nappac­caya­bhesaj­ja­parik­khā­raṃ adāsi so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji …"
msgstr "to whom you gave medicines he attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.30"
msgid "samāpajjati …"
msgstr "is attaining …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.31"
msgid "samāpanno …"
msgstr "has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.32"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī …"
msgstr "obtains …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.33"
msgid "vasī …"
msgstr "masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.34"
msgid "tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatanti sampajānamusā bhaṇantassa paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti thullaccayassa;"
msgstr "has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” then, if the listener understands, he commits a serious offense when three conditions are fulfilled;"

#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.100
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.35"
msgid "na paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti dukkaṭassa—"
msgstr "if the listener does not understand, he commits an offense of wrong conduct when three conditions are fulfilled … when seven conditions are fulfilled:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.36"
msgid "pubbevassa hoti musā bhaṇissanti,"
msgstr "before he has lied, he knows he is going to lie;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.37"
msgid "bhaṇantassa hoti musā bhaṇāmīti,"
msgstr "while lying, he knows he is lying;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.38"
msgid "bhaṇitassa hoti musā mayā bhaṇitanti,"
msgstr "after he has lied, he knows he has lied;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.39"
msgid "vinidhāya diṭṭhiṃ,"
msgstr "he misrepresents his view of what is true;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.40"
msgid "vinidhāya khantiṃ,"
msgstr "he misrepresents his belief of what is true;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.41"
msgid "vinidhāya ruciṃ,"
msgstr "he misrepresents his acceptance of what is true;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.42"
msgid "vinidhāya bhāvaṃ."
msgstr "he misrepresents his sentiment of what is true."

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
#. REF: sc170, ms1V_703
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.43"
msgid "Peyyā­la­panna­rasa­kaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The successive fifteen are finished."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.44"
msgid "Pac­ca­yap­paṭi­saṃ­yutta­vāraka­thā niṭṭhitā."
msgstr "The exposition of the section on that connected with requisites is finished."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:6.2.45"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhamma­cakka­peyyā­laṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The successive permutation series on superhuman qualities is finished."

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc171, pts-cs-bu-pj4.7, ms1V_704
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.2"
msgid "adhimānena,"
msgstr "if he overestimates himself;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.3"
msgid "anul­lapa­nādhip­pāyassa,"
msgstr "if he does not intend to make a claim;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.4"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.5"
msgid "khittacittassa,"
msgstr "if he is deranged;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.6"
msgid "vedanāṭṭassa,"
msgstr "if he is overwhelmed by pain;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.7"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. HTML: </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.8"
msgid "4.1. Vinīta­vatthu­uddāna­gāthā"
msgstr "Case rulings mnemonic list"

#. HTML: </h5><div class="uddana"><p>
#. VAR: Adhimāne → adhimānena (bj, pts1)
#. REF: sc172, ms1V_705,  
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.9"
msgid "Adhimāne araññamhi,"
msgstr "About overestimation, in the wilderness,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.10"
msgid "piṇ­ḍo­paj­jhāriyā­patho;"
msgstr "Almsfood, a preceptor, behavior;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.11"
msgid "Saṃyojanā rahodhammā,"
msgstr "Fetters, qualities in private,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.12"
msgid "vihāro paccupaṭṭhito."
msgstr "A dwelling, attended on."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc173, ms1V_706
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.13"
msgid "Na dukkaraṃ viriyamathopi maccuno,"
msgstr "Not difficult, energy, fear of death,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.14"
msgid "Bhāyāvuso vippaṭisāri sammā;"
msgstr "Remorseful friend, rightly;"

#. HTML: <br>
#. REF: pts-vp-en1.172
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.15"
msgid "Viriyena yogena ārādhanāya,"
msgstr "By energy, by exertion,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.16"
msgid "Atha vedanāya adhivāsanā duve."
msgstr "Two on the enduring of feeling."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc174, ms1V_707
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.17"
msgid "Brāhmaṇe pañca vatthūni,"
msgstr "Five stories on a brahmin,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.18"
msgid "aññaṃ byākaraṇā tayo;"
msgstr "Three on declaring final knowledge;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.19"
msgid "Agārāvaraṇā kāmā,"
msgstr "House, rejected sense-pleasures,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.20"
msgid "rati cāpi apakkami."
msgstr "And delight, set out."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc175, ms1V_708
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.21"
msgid "Aṭṭhi pesi ubho gāvaghātakā,"
msgstr "Bone, lump: both are cattle-butchers,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.22"
msgid "Piṇḍo sākuṇiko nicchavi orabbhi;"
msgstr "A morsel is a poultry-butcher, a sheep-butcher is flayed;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.23"
msgid "Asi ca sūkariko satti māgavi,"
msgstr "And a pig-butcher and sword, a deer-hunter and knife,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.24"
msgid "Usu ca kāraṇiko sūci sārathi."
msgstr "And a torturer and arrow, a horse trainer and needle."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc176, ms1V_709
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.25"
msgid "Yo ca sibbīyati sūcako hi so,"
msgstr "And a slanderer is sewn,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.26"
msgid "Aṇḍabhāri ahu gāmakūṭako;"
msgstr "A corrupt magistrate with testicles as burden;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.27"
msgid "Kūpe nimuggo hi so pāradāriko,"
msgstr "An adulterer submerged in a pit,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.28"
msgid "Gūthakhādī ahu duṭṭhabrāhmaṇo."
msgstr "An eater of dung was a wicked brahmin."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc177, ms1V_710
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.29"
msgid "Nicchavitthī aticārinī ahu,"
msgstr "A flayed woman was an adulteress,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.30"
msgid "Maṅgulitthī ahu ikkhaṇitthikā;"
msgstr "An ugly woman was a fortune-teller;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.31"
msgid "Okilinī hi sapat­taṅ­gā­rokiri,"
msgstr "A sweltering woman scattered coals on a co-wife,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.32"
msgid "Sīsacchinno ahu coraghātako."
msgstr "A beheaded man was an executioner."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc178, ms1V_711
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.33"
msgid "Bhikkhu bhikkhunī sikkhamānā,"
msgstr "A monk, a nun, a trainee nun,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.34"
msgid "Sāmaṇero atha sāmaṇerikā;"
msgstr "A novice monk, then a novice nun;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.35"
msgid "Kassapassa vinayasmiṃ pabbajaṃ,"
msgstr "These having gone forth in the training of Kassapa"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.36"
msgid "Pāpakam­ma­makariṃsu tāvade."
msgstr "Did bad deeds just then."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc179, ms1V_712
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.37"
msgid "Tapodā rājagahe yuddhaṃ,"
msgstr "The Tapodā in Rājagaha, battle,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.38"
msgid "nāgānogāhanena ca;"
msgstr "And with the plunging in of elephants;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.39"
msgid "Sobhito arahaṃ bhikkhu,"
msgstr "The perfected monk Sobhita"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:7.40"
msgid "pañca­kap­pasataṃ sareti."
msgstr "Recalls five hundred eons."

#. HTML: </p></div><h3>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.0"
msgid "4.2. Vinītavatthu"
msgstr "Case details, part 1"

#. HTML: </h3><p>
#. REF: sc180, pts-cs-bu-pj4.8.1, pts-vp-en1.173, ms1V_713
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu adhimānena aññaṃ byākāsi."
msgstr "At one time a monk declared final knowledge because of overestimation."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.2"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi—"
msgstr "He became remorseful, thinking,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.3"
msgid "“bhagavatā sikkhāpadaṃ paññattaṃ."
msgstr "“The Master has laid down a training rule."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.4"
msgid "Kacci nu kho ahaṃ pārājikaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno”ti?"
msgstr "Could it be that I’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.5"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "He told the Master."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.1.6"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, adhimānenā”ti. #1"
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who overestimates himself.”"

#. HTML: </p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc181, pts-cs-bu-pj4.8.2, ms1V_714, pts-vp-pli3.101
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu paṇidhāya araññe viharati—"
msgstr "At one time a monk lived in the wilderness"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.2"
msgid "“evaṃ maṃ jano sambhāvessatī”ti."
msgstr "because he wanted people to esteem him."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.3"
msgid "Taṃ jano sambhāvesi."
msgstr "People esteemed him."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.4"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.5"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa."
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion."

#. HTML: <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.6"
msgid "Na ca, bhikkhave, paṇidhāya araññe vatthabbaṃ."
msgstr "But, monks, you should not live in the wilderness because of a wish."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.7"
msgid "Yo vaseyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti. #2"
msgstr "If you do, you commit an offense of wrong conduct.”"

#. HTML: </span> </p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc182, ms1V_715
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.8"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu paṇidhāya piṇḍāya carati—"
msgstr "At one time a monk was walking for almsfood"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.9"
msgid "“evaṃ maṃ jano sambhāvessatī”ti."
msgstr "because he wanted people to esteem him."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.10"
msgid "Taṃ jano sambhāvesi."
msgstr "People esteemed him."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.11"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.12"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa."
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion."

#. HTML: <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.13"
msgid "Na ca, bhikkhave, paṇidhāya piṇḍāya caritabbaṃ."
msgstr "But, monks, you should not walk for almsfood because of a wish."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.2.14"
msgid "Yo careyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti. #3"
msgstr "If you do, you commit an offense of wrong conduct.”"

#. HTML: </span> </p><p>
#. REF: sc183, pts-cs-bu-pj4.8.3, ms1V_716
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a monk said to another monk,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.2"
msgid "“ye, āvuso, amhākaṃ upajjhāyassa saddhivihārikā sabbeva arahanto”ti."
msgstr "“Those who are pupils of our preceptor are all perfected ones.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.3"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.4"
msgid "“kiṃcitto tvaṃ, bhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "“What was your intention, monk?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.5"
msgid "“Ullapa­nā­dhip­pāyo ahaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“I wanted to make a claim, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.6"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.7"
msgid "āpatti thullaccayassā”ti. #4"
msgstr "but there’s a serious offense.”"

#. HTML: </p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc184, pts-vp-en1.174, ms1V_717
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.8"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a monk said to another monk,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.9"
msgid "“ye, āvuso, amhākaṃ upajjhāyassa antevāsikā sabbeva mahiddhikā mahānubhāvā”ti."
msgstr "“Those who are students of our preceptor all have great supernormal power.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.10"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.11"
msgid "“kiṃcitto tvaṃ, bhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "“What was your intention, monk?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.12"
msgid "“Ullapa­nā­dhip­pāyo ahaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“I wanted to make a claim, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.13"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.3.14"
msgid "āpatti thullaccayassā”ti. #5"
msgstr "but there’s a serious offense.”"

#. HTML: </p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc185, pts-cs-bu-pj4.8.4, ms1V_718
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu paṇidhāya caṅkamati …"
msgstr "At one time a monk walked up and down because he wanted people to esteem him …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.2"
msgid "paṇidhāya tiṭṭhati …"
msgstr "stood because he wanted people to esteem him …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.3"
msgid "paṇidhāya nisīdati …"
msgstr "sat because he wanted people to esteem him …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.4"
msgid "paṇidhāya seyyaṃ kappeti—"
msgstr "laid down"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.5"
msgid "“evaṃ maṃ jano sambhāvessatī”ti."
msgstr "because he wanted people to esteem him."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.6"
msgid "Taṃ jano sambhāvesi."
msgstr "People esteemed him."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.7"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.8"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa."
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion."

#. HTML: <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.9"
msgid "Na ca, bhikkhave, paṇidhāya seyyā kappetabbā."
msgstr "But, monks, you should not walk up and down … stand … sit … lie down because of a wish."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.4.10"
msgid "Yo kappeyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti. #6–‍9"
msgstr "If you do, you commit an offense of wrong conduct.”"

#. HTML: </span></p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc186, pts-cs-bu-pj4.8.5, ms1V_719
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.5.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu aññatarassa bhikkhuno uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ ullapati."
msgstr "At one time a monk claimed a superhuman quality to another monk:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.5.2"
msgid "Sopi evamāha—“mayhampi, āvuso, saṃyojanā pahīnā”ti."
msgstr "“I’ve abandoned the fetters.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.5.3"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.5.4"
msgid "“āpattiṃ tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āpanno pārājikan”ti. #10"
msgstr "“You’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

#. HTML: </p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc187, pts-cs-bu-pj4.8.6, ms1V_720
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.6.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu rahogato uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ ullapati."
msgstr "At one time a monk claimed a superhuman quality in private."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.6.2"
msgid "Paracittavidū bhikkhu taṃ bhikkhuṃ apasādesi—"
msgstr "Another monk, knowing the mind of that monk, criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.6.3"
msgid "“mā, āvuso, evarūpaṃ abhaṇi."
msgstr "“Don’t say that;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.6.4"
msgid "Nattheso tuyhan”ti."
msgstr "you haven’t got it.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:8.6.5"
